  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continue a Journey of Treachery...</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755719711\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755719711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755719711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Continue DNA in Season 2 Episode 2 as Leo continues his journey to avenge his wife Luna, where he must then pass the dangerous volcanic mountains of Papura to seek out Terius.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/b6fc0369e2b96ca85926bd668d33be99.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enter Scorching Papura...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through the unforgiving volcanic lands of Papura as Leo continues searches for Terius.<br><br></li><li>Play through rewarding challenges fueled by vengeance.<br><br></li><li> Fight against ruthless Papura creatures that have been under the control of Onaclov...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/a650b07ac40476bc7d275bb802a3542c.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fuel Your Vengeance...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick back up this season with DNA's epic 2D Beat'em up gameplay with new abilities to acquire!<br><br></li><li>Experience a challenging gameplay formula building upon last season's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Battle diverse creatures as you make your way through the treacherous volcanic lands of Papura. </li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/50b9a44bfa304c30884bdebac8641d36.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Nemesis.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in Season 2: Episode 2 of DNA.<br><br></li><li>Search for your great nemesis Terius, in a challenging level of intense difficulty and grit.<br><br></li><li> Fight through a volcanic world full of dangerous creatures native to the lands of Papura... </li></ul></i>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continue a Journey of Treachery...</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755719711\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755719711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755719711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Continue DNA in Season 2 Episode 2 as Leo continues his journey to avenge his wife Luna, where he must then pass the dangerous volcanic mountains of Papura to seek out Terius.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/b6fc0369e2b96ca85926bd668d33be99.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enter Scorching Papura...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through the unforgiving volcanic lands of Papura as Leo continues searches for Terius.<br><br></li><li>Play through rewarding challenges fueled by vengeance.<br><br></li><li> Fight against ruthless Papura creatures that have been under the control of Onaclov...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/a650b07ac40476bc7d275bb802a3542c.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fuel Your Vengeance...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick back up this season with DNA's epic 2D Beat'em up gameplay with new abilities to acquire!<br><br></li><li>Experience a challenging gameplay formula building upon last season's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Battle diverse creatures as you make your way through the treacherous volcanic lands of Papura. </li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964840/extras/50b9a44bfa304c30884bdebac8641d36.avif?t=1755719711\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Nemesis.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in Season 2: Episode 2 of DNA.<br><br></li><li>Search for your great nemesis Terius, in a challenging level of intense difficulty and grit.<br><br></li><li> Fight through a volcanic world full of dangerous creatures native to the lands of Papura... </li></ul></i>",
